{"tid":228332,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想請教下大汗嘅巴打","createTime":"2017-05-03T20:08:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T19:40:39.000Z","uid":15174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9cf2b7efd397be914f0e19fa52250ef308b6ecd","tid":228332,"uid":15174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T20:08:40.000Z","msg":"小弟都係好撚大汗<br />\n宜家哩啲天氣  行多兩步都已經成身濕哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n假如您哋同女朋友出街嗰時都係咁<br />\n您會點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時手前臂有汗  拖嗰時會整到佢隻手都濕埋<br />\n成身汗又唔攬得...多汗嗰時又易臭...<br />\n搞到有拖都唔敢拍...我會唔會太毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大汗嘅您哋係會選擇淨係行有冷氣嘅地方<br />\n定係有其他應對方法減少以上所講嘅情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以分享下<br />\n小弟虛心受教"},{"pid":"34720e57299264027d840853a70075c6f3ff10f3","tid":228332,"uid":88556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T20:14:46.000Z","msg":"大汗真係好撚煩<br />\n行一陣都濕撚曬"},{"pid":"3115797dd956ac7b06de74296fbb3ff5a63cb0eb","tid":228332,"uid":104333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T20:16:09.000Z","msg":"件衫唔夠一個鐘就臭<br />\n好在女友鼻塞"},{"pid":"2fb18a39b138b0140ab74031da0dd05ceca18832","tid":228332,"uid":47797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T20:39:27.000Z","msg":"一見到有商場 就去涼下冷氣再行 唔撚係的話真係行多陣就成身出哂汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21758dcd763f0648a150764d29de3bad9020f86","tid":228332,"uid":15174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T22:12:29.000Z","msg":"所以我先想知各位巴打有咩應對方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e5a0dae0b8a1a6e6425a3bad86d53c2ebd7e7b","tid":228332,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T22:23:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1edef78110d42891d2e1c0776be0955048e27fd7","tid":2